'''Glimetoto afahyɛ''' yɛ afehyia [[afahyɛ]] a ahenfo ne wɔn manfo a wɔn wɔ Adaklu a ɛwɔ Frao Mnatam no mu di wɔ Ghana<ref>https://ghanaemberlin.de/travel-tourism/festival/</ref>. Wɔn a wodi no ne Kpeve, Klikor ne Tsohor<ref>https://www.easytrackghana.com/cultural-overview-ghana-festivals.php</ref>. Wodi afahyɛ no wɔ Bosome a ɛtɔ dubaako no mu<ref>https://www.hugedomains.com/domain_profile.cfm?d=ghanaculturepolitics&e=com</ref><ref>https://visitvoltaregion.com/festivals/</ref>.

== Afa hyɛ ==
Wɔ afahyɛ no bre mu no, Ahenfo ne wɔn manfo bɔ dwa data ma wosiesie ntawantawa di baiara. Wɔsan nso da wɔn nananom akokoduru a wɔdaa no adi no adi denam asafo nnwomtoɔ, twenebɔ ne asa ahorɔw so<ref>https://touringghana.com/volta-region/</ref><ref>http://h2829516.stratoserver.net/tourism/index.html</ref>.

== Mfasoɔ ==
Afahyɛ no yɛ nea wɔde kae bere a Adaklufo no tuu firii Notsie a ɛwɔ Togoman mu no de baa faako a wɔn wo sesei no<ref>https://www.fiandadghanalimited.com/glimetotoza-festival/</ref>.

